    "Virgin flies were housed individually and kept in behavioural incubators under a 12 h:12 h light:dark cycling; individual males were paired with a pheromone insensitive and blind (PIBL) female to encourage longer courtship sessions-see Supplementary Table 1 for more info on genotype.",
